      conditions:
      - state: ok ✅
        type: NoClusterDataConflict
      deleted:
        state: ok ✅
      name: appset-deploy-rbd
      namespace: e2e-appset-deploy-rbd
      protectedPVCs:
      - conditions:
        - state: ok ✅
          type: DataReady
        - description: Observed generation 1 does not match object generation 2
          state: "stale \U0001F7E0"
          type: ClusterDataProtected
